title: Swarovski Santa's Elf On Sleigh Dark Multicolor One Size
description: A Swarovski tribute to Santa's Little Helpers: Sitting on a polished metal sleigh, this crystal elf seems to be taking some time off between present-making. In classic festive green, red, and sparkling clear crystal and 272 facets, he is a beautiful addition to a decoration set. His delicately crafted pointy ears and his happy face brought out in black and pink crystal details make this little helper the perfect festive figurine.
